<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Contagious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Contagious,</orth> poisonous, pestilential, pernicious: <cit><quote>c. fogs,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 90</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>breath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 56</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this night, whose black c. breath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 4, 33</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>clouds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.222" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 222</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>prison,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 36</bibl></cit> (Pistol's speech). <cit><quote>clouds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 31</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>darkness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sickness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 26</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>blastments,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 42</bibl></cit>. Misapplied by Fluellen: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 22</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>